name: FLORAL MEGA DOODLE #2
description: FLORAL MEGA DOODLES is a series of digital doodle drawings based on flowers I find in bloom on the numerous walks I do in nature be it the countryside or public gardens or if I’m lucky through the concrete jungle. Nature loves to express itself and inspire and share its optimistic bounty. In the challenging times we live a flower is a nice antidote to a closed heart in whatever form that takes.
